data.description: Welcome home is what this turnkey home says when you walk in the door! There is so much this beautiful home offers, & if a buyer qualifies, one can ASSUME the current loan w/an all time low interest rate at 2.25%!!! YES, you heard right, 2.25% interest rate, which will save you thousands of $$$$ over time, (buyer to verify terms & conditions). This turnkey home offers 3 BDs (all on the main floor), 2 spacious BAs, 1 w/a walk in shower, & a lg. loft area which can be a bonus room, gym, office, hobby room, or add another bedroom, your choice. There is also another bonus room/family room on the main floor, giving you more space to make your own. The beautiful lg. open kitchen has ample room, w/granite counter tops, a breakfast bar, a dbl. oven, & lots of cupboard space. The home also offers reverse osmosis (in kitchen) for great tasting water, & a whole house water filtration/UV conditioning system! The home is situated on 2+ acres of usable land, bring the horses if you so desire, along w/newer fencing around the back side of the property, along w/a fenced in vegetable garden area! The home offers solar, w/smart technology features, a dog door also w/smart features, & a newer metal roof so you are set for years to come, did I mention the whole house generator, yes it has this too! Also included are newer dbl. paned thermal windows throughout! If you wish to enjoy the outdoors & what beautiful Lush Meadows Estates has to offer, you are just around the corner from Dawn Lake!
